The paper deals with iris recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves image processing techniques such as wavelet transform and Hilbert transform, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). The Log-Gabor iris encoder is a well-known technique in iris recognition, so it is likely that the paper would be categorized under cs.LG (Log-Gabor). Finally, the paper involves encoding techniques, which are related to information theory (cs.IT).
